 />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278690&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278690%26csid%3D261_341&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQynXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=46295e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278690&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"屌你，遊行多左係證明民憤有增無減丫，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64a0c6e1cdb090691702dbf3f4dc6681dbe780f","tid":1957430,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:10:25.000Z","msg":"畜牲林鄭冚家剷死三代"},{"pid":"ee544dd4c105a8440329650ecbce5a2041d5fd28","tid":1957430,"uid":119299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"本文講遊行集會，都冇講係遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n樓主老屈遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6613e3a150460ef25907d93c6dd8373f6931c0","tid":1957430,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"[引用] 香港特首人工每日高達$14274<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957491</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff90fa0d59897a47fb4638db0b36c22de3ade497","tid":1957430,"uid":269137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14a81d7b596cee90374e76a40518b38bae399291","tid":1957430,"uid":14422,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"我舉例說，本港去年有超過1.6萬次催淚彈發放，是1997年的1.6萬倍，證明市民所享的自由有減無增。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"半澤君,0乘幾多倍都係0啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9972d5b31f12c5149945cead888fced619e5f9dc","tid":1957430,"uid":339472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0